proposal: Hey there! Noticed your project champions decentralization, code as law, and participant responsibility - a solid foundation for any blockchain endeavor. With 39 holders on the ETH network, congrats on building a community that values these principles. If you're looking to empower them further, our DEX and Lottery tools could be the perfect fit, allowing anyone in your community to deploy and share in the revenue. Let's decentralize the fun and profits together!
